---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | Floors To You OKC" description="How Floors To You OKC collects, uses, and protects your personal information.">
  <Breadcrumb items={[{ name: 'Home', url: '/' }, { name: 'Privacy', url: '/privacy' }]} />
  <section class="container-x py-12 max-w-3xl prose-brand">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Floors To You OKC respects your privacy. We collect personal information (name, email, phone, address) only when you submit a quote request, financing application, or contact form. We use that information to respond to your request, schedule estimates, and process orders.</p>
    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>Contact details you provide via our forms; project details you share with our team; and basic analytics about how visitors use the site.</p>
    <h2>How We Use It</h2>
    <p>To respond to inquiries, schedule estimates and installations, send order updates, and improve our website. We do not sell personal information to third parties.</p>
    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use cookies to operate the site and measure performance. You can disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this policy? Call us at (405) 913-7381 or visit our showroom at 4020 W Reno Ave, Oklahoma City, OK 73107.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
